Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Can now! Can now! 相信就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,900)}因为是你给出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:50.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,1900)}所以我会笑着接受
